                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14473128" author="melix" created="Fri, 20 Jul 2012 07:50:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reason is that the &lt;tt&gt;GroovyObject&lt;/tt&gt; interface is added after the type checker is run, so the class node doesn&apos;t have &lt;tt&gt;GroovyObject&lt;/tt&gt; in its interface list. I should implement a special case for this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
